### AI-102 REST API — Azure AI Vision
### Module 4, Lab 4.1: Analyze Images
### Use with VS Code REST Client extension

@endpoint = {{$dotenv AI_SERVICES_ENDPOINT}}
@apiKey = {{$dotenv AI_SERVICES_KEY}}

### ============================================
### Image Analysis 4.0 — Tags, Caption, Objects
### EXAM TIP: Know the visualFeatures parameter options
### ============================================

POST {{endpoint}}/computervision/imageanalysis:analyze?api-version=2024-02-01&features=tags,caption,objects,read,people,denseCaptions
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "url": "https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-services/computer-vision/media/quickstarts/presentation.png"
}

### ============================================
### OCR — Read Text from Image
### EXAM TIP: This is the newer unified Read API
### ============================================

POST {{endpoint}}/computervision/imageanalysis:analyze?api-version=2024-02-01&features=read
Content-Type: application/json
Ocp-Apim-Subscription-Key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "url": "https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-services/computer-vision/media/quickstarts/handwritten-text.jpg"
}
